## Workflow Steps

### Step 1: Gather Yesterday's Activity

1. **Query completed work (last 24 hours):**
   ```bash
   # Get work items completed or updated yesterday
   yesterday=$(date -d "yesterday" +%Y-%m-%d)
   az boards query --wiql "SELECT [System.Id], [System.Title], [System.State], [System.AssignedTo] FROM WorkItems WHERE [System.TeamProject] = '{{ work_tracking.project }}' AND [System.IterationPath] UNDER '{{ work_tracking.iteration_format.format(project=work_tracking.project, sprint='CURRENT_SPRINT') }}' AND [System.ChangedDate] >= '$yesterday'" --output json
